    "An incomplete package may pass planning verification but may not be approved.",
    "A present artifact must exist and pass its declared verifier.",
    "Every present artifact records and matches its exact byte_count and sha256; file existence alone never closes an artifact.",
    "Successor carry-forward is closed by BaselineLineage.v4 and cannot infer compatibility from a matching filename or predecessor status.",
