    "P0A-Q0 materializes the two-stage environment proof, Q0/gate/feature/process/resource catalogs and offline fixtures without claiming a live Q0 result.",
    "A complete inventory is approval-eligible only after the checked-in standalone normative package verifier returns a matching structured pass result.",
    "A missing artifact must not be silently treated as present; a partially materialized artifact is explicitly in_progress and remains approval-blocking.",
    "Review evidence is non-normative and cannot change the narrative specification content hash.",
    "A narrative specification ID maps to exactly one validated byte sequence; any narrative byte change requires a new narrative ID.",
    "Each normative artifact has its own immutable artifact ID, schema version and content hash; a present artifact cannot be rewritten in place.",
    "The final BaselineManifest instance is created only after every other normative artifact and the preliminary consistency review are present and green.",
    "BaselineManifest binds the frozen package_review_head; the later manifest-closure review appends to that chain without changing manifest bytes.",
    "BaselineApprovalRecord binds an approval_review_head that is a verified successor of package_review_head and includes the manifest-closure review.",
    "No BaselineApprovalRecord may exist until approval_eligible is true."
